      <span class="step-num" style="color:var(--color-blue)">02</span>
      <span class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--color-blue)">Phase 1 · Live in it · The First Door</span>
      <h1 class="display-xl step-hero__title">First-Time Home Buyer</h1>
      <p class="lede step-hero__lede">This is the first door — the step where you stop paying someone else's mortgage and start building your own equity. For most people, the first home is the single most important financial move they'll make, and it's where the Stairway truly begins to climb.</p>
